These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Flower: aconite, azalea
Music-Genre: funk, country
Nationality: argentine, japanese
Color: light-blue, grey
1. Color:grey is on the left or right of Nationality:japanese##3
2. Flower:azalea is in an even position##4
3. Music-Genre:country == Flower:aconite##1
4. Color:grey is on the right of Color:light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Flower      | aconite  | azalea   |
| Music-Genre   | country     | funk   |
| Nationality         | japanese | argentine |
| Color     | light-blue | grey    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Job: journalist, software-developer
Beverage: fanta, lemonade
Cigar: alhambra, bongani
Color: mauve, yellow
1. Cigar:bongani is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:fanta == Color:yellow##1
3. Job:software-developer is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Job          | journalist     | software-developer |
| Beverage   | lemonade | fanta  |
| Cigar           | bongani         | alhambra     |
| Color     | mauve   | yellow    |

