Hobby: gardening, dancing
Flower: sunflower, daffodil
Food: pepper, tomato
1. Food:tomato is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:dancing is on the far left or far right##3
3. Beverage:tea == Hobby:gardening##1
4. Flower:sunflower is on the left of Hobby:dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Beverage           | tea | milk    |
| Hobby   | gardening       | dancing |
| Flower           | sunflower         | daffodil    |
| Food         | pepper    | tomato   |

